"\n"
"<3.so>Lady Mipha! <4.pa>Watch THIS!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I, Seggin, the aptly named Demon Sergeant,<5.pa>\n"
"shall strike down<6.pa> the <7.se_co>Divine Beast Vah "
"Ruta<8.re_co>!<9.si_ch><10.te_si>"
