msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hmph! <2.pa>There is no way we would ask for\n"
"your help now, after all this time and\n"
"after all that has happened!\n"
"So says I, Seggin, the Demon Sergeant!<3.pa>\n"
"Even if this body of mine is destroyed...\n"
"\n"
"I will drown <4.se_co>Ruta<5.re_co> in <6.se_co>shock arrows "
"<7.re_co>myself!<8.pa>\n"
"And in doing so, <9.se_co>Lady Mipha<10.re_co>'s regrets\n"
"shall be alleviated.\n"
"<11.so>If you understand anything of courage,\n"
"then get out of my way at once!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: sound
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You have acted so cold and unconcerned\n"
"about the harm that befell Lady Mipha...\n"
"\n"
"But no matterâ€”it is too late now.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I shall be the one to shoot <2.se_co>Ruta<3.re_co> down.<4.pa>\n"
"So it was decided by the Zora council!\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>Just stay out of my way!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk07"
msgid "<1.so>You! <2.pa>Link!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid "<1.so>You again?!"
msgstr ""

