#. 10: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk12"
msgid ""
"<1.te_si><2.so>AAAARGH! <3.pa>What did you say?!<4.te_si>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I, Seggin, used to strike fear into the\n"
"hearts of demons<5.pa> just by setting foot\n"
"onto the battlefield!\n"
"<6.so>Stopping the <7.se_co>Divine Beast Vah Ruta<8.re_co><9.pa>\n"
"will be simpler than taking a fish from\n"
"a baby... <10.pa>No trouble at all, I say!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk13"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Still... <2.pa>According to my fortune today,\n"
"I should be cautious of injury.\n"
"\n"
"In light of that, I think it would be for the\n"
"best if I call it a day."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk14"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I still greatly wish to dispel <2.se_co>Lady Mipha<3.re_co>'s\n"
"lingering regrets, <4.pa>but I fear it is time to\n"
"retire for a while.\n"
"If I were to fall due to lack of sleep,<5.pa>\n"
"that would only sadden Lady Mipha\n"
"further still..."
msgstr ""

