msgctxt "talk19"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You! <2.pa>Link!<3.pa> I have avenged Lady Mipha!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>Actually...I wish I could say that, but it is\n"
"not true. <5.pa>To think you of all people would\n"
"be the one to appease the <6.se_co>Divine Beast<7.re_co>...\n"
"<8.so>What happened to Lady Mipha was\n"
"unfortunate...<9.pa>but I understand now.\n"
"I no longer have reason to despise you."
msgstr ""

