msgctxt "talk20"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Link... <2.pa>I never thought you would be the\n"
"one to appease the <3.se_co>Divine Beast<4.re_co>...\n"
"\n"
"Ever since Lady Mipha was swallowed\n"
"up by the <5.se_co>Divine Beast<6.re_co> 100 years ago...<7.pa>\n"
"I have hated you with all my heart.\n"
"<8.so>But it would seem my anger\n"
"was misplaced."
msgstr ""

