msgctxt "talk22"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Huh?!<2.pa> A Hylian!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I am sorry, but the <3.se_co>Zora's Domain<4.re_co> council<5.pa>\n"
"does not take kindly to Hylians.\n"
"\n"
"I advise you to not stick around here\n"
"for too long.\n"
"\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"..."
